Patina, rust freckles, and kintsugi-like fissures across the bell; thick chain and clapper centered. Far below, a lone, coat-clad figure stands soft-focused among dark firs and slate hills. Atmosphere: cold blue-grey mist, breath of wind, tension right before the strike—endurance, time, gravity. Photoreal clarity, shallow depth of field, natural film grain, 9:16 vertical. Negative: text/logos, neon, crowds, glossy HDR, extra people.
